And the three of you see him pull a device out of his pocket.

1206
00:59:50,180 --> 00:59:55,300
It's got like a sign reading that goes across of it.

1207
00:59:55,300 --> 00:59:57,300
And it's got lights up on the top.

1208
00:59:57,300 --> 00:59:58,019
And he's looking at it.

1209
00:59:58,019 --> 01:00:00,019
He's like, yeah, okay, Seth,

1210
01:00:00,740 --> 01:00:02,100
Kath, it's time to go.

1211
