No, these people won't understand what just happened.

1215
01:00:11,540 --> 01:00:12,500
Where did he go?

1216
01:00:13,460 --> 01:00:16,900
Uh, back home.

1217
01:00:17,860 --> 01:00:18,360
Back home.

1218
01:00:20,740 --> 01:00:22,580
Are you guys going to go back home now?

1219
01:00:23,300 --> 01:00:23,940
Yep.

1220
01:00:23,940 --> 01:00:30,340
And you see him pull what looks like a small crossbow out of his hand,

1221
01:00:30,340 --> 01:00:32,900
