1242
01:01:33,779 --> 01:01:36,819
was the last thing in the world he hadn't learned.

1243
01:01:38,099 --> 01:01:39,619
That's amazing, Sully.

1244
01:01:39,619 --> 01:01:43,539
So, I think your key string saved the day.

